Templates.Name: StableDiffusion
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: The stable-diffusion model is a text-to-image diffusion model that can generate highly realistic images based on textual input. It utilizes latent variables and diffusion processes to achieve this.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion Turbo
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: SD-Turbo is a fast generative text-to-image model that can synthesize photorealistic images from a text prompt in a single network evaluation. We release SD-Turbo as a research artifact, and to study small, distilled text-to-image models

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion 2
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 2 is a latent diffusion model conditioned on the penultimate text embeddings of a CLIP ViT-H/14 text encoder.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion XL
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: The SDXL model is a text-to-image generative AI model that can create high-resolution images with a size of 1024x1024 pixels. It takes text descriptions as input and generates corresponding images as output. The model aims to create beautiful and realistic images based on the provided textual prompts.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion XL Refiner
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: SDXL consists of an ensemble of experts pipeline for latent diffusion: In a first step, the base model is used to generate (noisy) latents, which are then further processed with a refinement model specialized for the final denoising steps. Note that this model can not be used as a standalone module.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion XL Turbo
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: SDXL-Turbo is a distilled version of SDXL 1.0, trained for real-time synthesis. SDXL-Turbo is based on a novel training method called Adversarial Diffusion Distillation (ADD) (see the technical report), which allows sampling large-scale foundational image diffusion models in 1 to 4 steps at high image quality. This approach uses score distillation to leverage large-scale off-the-shelf image diffusion models as a teacher signal and combines this with an adversarial loss to ensure high image fidelity even in the low-step regime of one or two sampling steps.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion XL Lightning
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: SDXL-Lightning is a lightning-fast text-to-image generation model. It can generate high-quality 1024px images in a few steps. For more information, please refer to our research paper: SDXL-Lightning: Progressive Adversarial Diffusion Distillation. We open-source the model as part of the research.

Templates.Name: Stable Cascade
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: This model is built upon the Würstchen architecture and its main difference to other models like Stable Diffusion is that it is working at a much smaller latent space. Why is this important? The smaller the latent space, the faster you can run inference and the cheaper the training becomes.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion 3
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3 is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer (MMDiT) text-to-image model that features greatly improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion 3 Turbo
Templates.Author: Amuse
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3 is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer (MMDiT) text-to-image model that features greatly improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency.

Templates.Name: FLUX.1 Dev

Templates.Description: FLUX is a of a 12-billion parameter rectified flow transformer designed to generate detailed and high-quality images directly from text descriptions. This model offers impressive capabilities in transforming prompts into vivid and accurate visual representations.

Templates.Name: FLUX.1 Schnell

Templates.Description: FLUX Distilled is a distilled version of a 12-billion parameter rectified flow transformer designed to generate detailed and high-quality images directly from text descriptions. This model offers impressive capabilities in transforming prompts into vivid and accurate visual representations.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion
Templates.Author: RunwayML
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion is a text-to-image latent diffusion model created by the researchers and engineers from CompVis, Stability AI and LAION. It is trained on 512x512 images from a subset of the LAION-5B database. LAION-5B is the largest, freely accessible multi-modal dataset that currently exists.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion XL Turbo
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: SDXL-Turbo is a distilled version of SDXL 1.0, trained for real-time synthesis. SDXL-Turbo is based on a novel training method called Adversarial Diffusion Distillation (ADD) (see the technical report), which allows sampling large-scale foundational image diffusion models in 1 to 4 steps at high image quality.

Templates.Name: StableCascade

Templates.Description: ToonYou based Locomotion text-to-video AI model, enabling seamless video generation from text, images, or videos. It combines motion synthesis & frame interpolation for smooth, high-quality outputs.

Templates.Name: StableDiffusion (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: RunwayML
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion is a text-to-image latent diffusion model created by the researchers and engineers from CompVis, Stability AI and LAION. It is trained on 512x512 images from a subset of the LAION-5B database. LAION-5B is the largest, freely accessible multi-modal dataset that currently exists.

Templates.Name: SDXL (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: SDXL consists of an ensemble of experts pipeline for latent diffusion: In a first step, the base model is used to generate (noisy) latents, which are then further processed with a refinement model (available here: https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-refiner-1.0/) specialized for the final denoising steps.

Templates.Name: Dreamshaper Lightning (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: DreamShaper Lightning is a general purpose SDXL-Lightning model that aims at doing everything well, photos, art, anime, manga. It's designed to go against other general purpose models and pipelines like Midjourney and DALL-E.

Templates.Name: SDXL Turbo (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: SDXL-Turbo is a distilled version of SDXL 1.0, trained for real-time synthesis. SDXL-Turbo is based on a novel training method called Adversarial Diffusion Distillation (ADD) (see the technical report), which allows sampling large-scale foundational image diffusion models in 1 to 4 steps at high image quality.

Templates.Name: SD3 Medium (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3 Medium is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer with improvements (MMDiT-X) text-to-image model that features improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency.

Templates.Name: SD3.5 Medium (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3.5 Medium is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer with improvements (MMDiT-X) text-to-image model that features improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency.

Templates.Name: SD3.5 (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3.5 Large is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer (MMDiT) text-to-image model that features improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency.

Templates.Name: SD3.5 Turbo (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: Stability AI
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion 3.5 Large Turbo is a Multimodal Diffusion Transformer (MMDiT) text-to-image model with Adversarial Diffusion Distillation (ADD) that features improved performance in image quality, typography, complex prompt understanding, and resource-efficiency, with a focus on fewer inference steps.

Templates.Name: FLUX.1-schnell (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: BlackForestLabs
Templates.Description: FLUX.1 [schnell] is a 12-billion parameter rectified flow transformer designed to generate detailed and high-quality images directly from text descriptions. This model offers impressive capabilities in transforming prompts into vivid and accurate visual representations.

Templates.Name: FLUX.1-Dev (AMDGPU)
Templates.Author: BlackForestLabs
Templates.Description: FLUX.1 [dev] is a 12-billion parameter rectified flow transformer designed to generate detailed and high-quality images directly from text descriptions. This model offers impressive capabilities in transforming prompts into vivid and accurate visual representations.

Templates.Name: Hyper SD

Templates.Description: Hyper-SD is one of the new State-of-the-Art diffusion model acceleration techniques. In this repository, we release the models distilled from SDXL Base 1.0 and Stable-Diffusion v1-5。

Templates.Name: SDXL Lightning
Templates.Author: ByteDance
Templates.Description: SDXL-Lightning is a lightning-fast text-to-image generation model. It can generate high-quality 1024px images in a few steps. For more information, please refer to our research paper: SDXL-Lightning: Progressive Adversarial Diffusion Distillation. We open-source the model as part of the research.

Templates.Name: SXZ Luma
Templates.Author: sadxzero
Templates.Description: This is anime-based semi-realistic mix of checkpoints and loras tweaked for good results on simple prompts. Model is fully compatible with all LoRA that I made and will make in the future.

Templates.Name: ToonYou
Templates.Author: Bradcatt
Templates.Description: Silly, stylish, and surprisingly cute! With a bit of detail and a cartoony feel, it keeps getting better!

Templates.Name: unStable Illusion
Templates.Author: Peli86
Templates.Description: Stable Diffusion checkpoint - Goal is to get better eyes and better light compared to v1. No need to prompt too much, basicly a beginner Checkpoint. Enjoy and share your creations, helps me to improve.

Templates.Name: YesMix
Templates.Author: zakp
Templates.Description: Anime Model, Upload 2.0 improves the balance between realistic and anime generation for more natural results. Works well with other LoRAs, and FastNegativeV2 embedding enhances image clarity. The NAI VAE is baked in, so no additional VAEs needed. Not recommended for LoRA training.

Templates.Name: Instruct Pix-2-Pix
Templates.Author: timbrooks
Templates.Description: InstructPix2Pix lets you edit images simply by giving it written instructions. Just provide an image and a prompt, and the model quickly makes the desired changes, delivering impressive, realistic edits in seconds.
